This is a concept file with following syntax for each concept.
# Wait for product cart page elements to visible
* Wait until element "xpath" "//a[text()='Proceed To Checkout']" is visible
* Wait until element "css" "table#cart_info_table td.cart_description a" is clickable

# Verify product has been added to cart page
* Scroll to element "css" "table#cart_info_table td.cart_description a"
* Verify that element "css" "table#cart_info_table td.cart_description a" contains stored text "productName"